node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Chase Hudson on September 16, 2021. May be an image of 2 people, indoor and text that says 'SHARED SSING M'.

node.text: my prized possession teenage heartbreak is officially out i can’t believe this is the first time that i can say that i’ve put out an entire body of work that both matches my vision and my persona. i wanted to give you guys something raw and from the heart as it gets. this album was an emotional journey for me, i had to bring myself back to dark places i would have liked to forget about and really made me reflect on them. this project is about every relationship i have gone through in my life whether it was good or bad they each taught me something very valuable in their own ways. i wanted to thank you guys all so much for supporting me each step of the way. its what wakes me up in the morning and let’s me rest at the end of the day, you motivate me to be a better person, to reach new heights, and to push through the dark times. i wanted to thank my amazing team over at interscope/geffen/immersive for being such a helping hand in this process for believing in my vision and for letting me bring it life. this album was a concept that i had for such a long time, i had kept all of my past to myself for years and today i let it all on the table. this is just the very beginning , a trailer for what i have in store. i love you all it’s heres to teenage heartbreak everyone

i’ve held onto this song for more than a year and I can’t be more proud of a record. I’m so happy that this is dropping —  it’s been my favorite project and such a dope music video as well. I wanted to remind y’all that I wouldn’t be able to do what I do today without you. Teenage Heartbreak the album is my greatest creation and here’s the first sprinkle of it. Let’s get it started babyyy🖤
“Partycrasher” music video directed by @mooch is out now only on my @facebook !!
